column5: A blond walks into Tim Horton's and orders a coffee.  All of a sudden she starts to jump up and down and scream "I won a motor-home, I won a motor-home!"  The girl behind the counter is confused, because she knows that a motor-home is NOT one of the prizes offered for this season's roll-up-the-rim contest.  She asks to see the winning cup.  "I'm sorry Ma'am'"she says after examining the rim.  "This says win a bagel"    Ha ha !!!!
